'''1980年夏季奥林匹克运动会[[曲棍球|曲棍球]]比赛'''是[[1980年夏季奥林匹克运动会|1980年夏季奥林匹克运动会]]的其中一个比赛项目，该项目于1980年7月20日至31日进行。女子曲棍球项目在该届比赛首次成为正式项目<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1096683/big-read-1980-zimbabwe-hockey|title=Zimbabwe's first Olympic gold and the forgotten hockey fairytale of 1980|work=Inside the Games|date=2020-07-26|accessdate=2020-09-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923194107/https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1096683/big-read-1980-zimbabwe-hockey|archivedate=2020-09-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

男子项目决赛中，印度队以4比3击败西班牙队，第八次夺得该项目冠军<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thehindu.com/sport/hockey/1980-olympics-india-sinks-spain-for-gold/article3649630.ece|title=1980 Olympics: India sinks Spain for gold|publisher=The Hindu|date=2012-07-17|accessdate=2020-09-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130219234322/https://www.thehindu.com/sport/hockey/1980-olympics-india-sinks-spain-for-gold/article3649630.ece|archivedate=2013-02-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。女子项目方面，津巴布韦队以循环赛3胜2平未负一场的战绩，爆冷夺得冠军，这是津巴布韦历史上的首枚奥运金牌<ref>{{cite book | title = Moscow Olympics 1980 – Zimbabwe Women's Hockey Gold Medallists | year = 1980 | location = Salisbury | publisher = Zimbabwe Olympic Committee | type = commemorative booklet | ref = [[津巴布韦奥林匹克委员会|Zimbabwe Olympic Committee]]}}</ref>。<ref name="SR">{{cite web |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/summer/1980/HOK/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417090354/https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/summer/1980/HOK/ |archive-date=2020-04-17 |title=Hockey at the 1980 Moscow Summer Games |work=Sports Reference |accessdate=2019-10-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

